go` and `file2.go`\\n- `TestGetAllChangedFilesBetweenTrees` (line 777) — can be deleted since the function is removed\\n\\n### 3. Handle `CondenseSessionByID` (doctor command)\\n\\n**File:** `cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_condensation.go` (line 743)\\n\\n`CondenseSessionByID` calls `CondenseSession` with `nil` committedFiles. When called from `entire doctor`, there's no specific commit to reference. Attribution will get `nil` committedFiles — handle this by either:\\n- Skipping non-agent attribution when committedFiles is nil (return empty set for non-agent files)\\n- This is acceptable since doctor is a salvage path, not the normal flow\\n\\n### 4. Remove dead code\\n\\n- Delete `getAllChangedFilesBetweenTrees` from `manual_commit_attribution.go`\\n- Delete `TestGetAllChangedFilesBetweenTrees` from `manual_commit_attribution_test.go`\\n\\n### 5. Remove timing instrumentation\\n\\nRemove the timing `logging.Info` calls and `\\\"time\\\"` import added during investigation from:\\n- `manual_commit_hooks.go` — PrepareCommitMsg and PostCommit timing logs\\n- `manual_commit_condensation.go` — CondenseSession timing logs\\n\\n## Files Modified\\n\\n- `cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_hooks.go` — `filesChangedInCommit` rewrite + remove timing logs\\n- `cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_attribution.go` — new param, remove `getAllChangedFilesBetweenTrees`\\n- `cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_condensation.go` — thread committedFiles through opts + remove timing logs\\n- `cmd/entire/cli/strategy/manual_commit_attribution_test.go` — update tests\\n\\n## Verification\\n\\n1. `mise run fmt && mise run lint && mise run test:ci`\\n2. Build binary, test on rust repo (~58k files): `time git commit -m 'test'` — expect <500ms\\n\"},\"sourceToolAssistantUUID\":\"aa38d4f4-e0ce-4683-a528-df65760c2865\"}\n{\"parentUuid\":\"c058d6af-906f-428d-b031-75ab862d5107\",\"isSidechain\":false,\"userType\":\"external\",\"cwd\":\"/Users/alex/workspace/cli/.worktrees/3\",\"sessio